Egbeda bụ ọchịchị ime obodo na Oyo State, Nigeria
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị n'obodo Egbeda
Egbeda local government e weputara Lagelu Local Government na 1989
Koodu nzi ozi nke ebe ahu bu 200109
O nwere mpaghara nke 191 km2 na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ nke 281,573 na ọnụ ọgụgụ afọ 2006.

Egbeda ime obodo na-ekewa n'ime ngalaba iri na otu: Erunmu, Ayede / Alugbo / Koloko, Owo Baale / Kasumu, Olodan / Ajiwogbo, Olodo / Kumapayi I, Olodo II, Olodo III, Osegere / Awaye, Egbeda, Olode / Alakia, na Olubadan Estate.
Onye isi oche a họpụtara ahọpụta na ndị kansụl 11 a họpụtara site na ngalaba ọ bụla na-eduzi Gọọmentị Obodo
Onye na-achị ọdịnala ugbu a bụ Elegbeda nke Egbeda Oba Victor Sunday Olatunde Okunola onye bụkwa onye otu Oyo State of Council of Obas and Chiefs.
